# Deploy via Docker Compose

自建 VPS 上的容器化部署方案。

## 前提

- 目标机器已安装 Docker + Docker Compose
- SSH 访问权限

## 部署

```bash
# 构建镜像
docker build -t {{NAME}}:{{VERSION}} .

# 启动
docker compose up -d strategy-bot

# 健康检查
docker compose ps strategy-bot
docker compose logs strategy-bot --tail 50
```

## docker-compose.yml 示例

```yaml
services:
  strategy-bot:
    image: {{NAME}}:{{VERSION}}
    restart: unless-stopped
    env_file: .env
    volumes:
      - ./config.json:/app/config.json
      - ./risk-profile.json:/app/risk-profile.json
      - strategy-data:/app/data
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "node", "-e", "process.exit(0)"]
      interval: 30s
      timeout: 10s
      retries: 3

volumes:
  strategy-data:
```

## 回滚

```bash
docker compose down strategy-bot
# 修改 image tag 为上一版本
docker compose up -d strategy-bot
```
